// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0341 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: e10d7c73-5c9a-51f7-b041-1b32a5fcc4a4

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:8*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
